name: 5037 artists in hic et nunc
description: All artists with at least one minted OBJKT before OBJKT#40000, ordered by the timestamp of their first mint. You should see a blue square if you ever minted an OBJKT: that's you! Click on the squares to see links to artists profiles and their genesis OBJKT. Copyminters and other reported users are shown in red. They seem to be a lot (211), but it's most probably only 3 or 4 guys. If you click twice in one of the bad guys he will disappear :)
